reviewText: Granddaughter loves this movie and it is smart enough for adults
This is a great movie. So cute. Keeps my 1 year old BOY entertained with all the songs
Disney makes a princess with big front teeth and long feet!  And shes firey!  Good story with humor and great music.
An all time favorite for the whole family! Fun songs!
I love how the price for the extras is the same as just buying the orginal movie itself. My son watches it at least once a day.
Wish I would've known that the Disney Movie Rewards were only for the UK, not the US.
Thank you! !  Its what i wanted!!
